/**
 * TypeScript definitions for Apple's MusicKit JS library.
 * 
 * MusicKit JS is Apple's official web framework for integrating Apple Music
 * into web applications. These types provide comprehensive coverage of the
 * MusicKit API, including:
 * 
 * - Music playback and queue management
 * - Apple Music API for catalog browsing
 * - User library and playlist management  
 * - Authentication and authorization
 * - Event handling and notifications
 * - Media item metadata and artwork
 * 
 * @see https://developer.apple.com/documentation/musickitjs
 * @see https://js-cdn.music.apple.com/musickit/v3/docs/
 */

